We respect your right to privacy and shares your concern about the security of any data you may create via our mobile application.
Your privacy is critically important to us. We don’t want to be creepy stalkers or evil spammers. We have a few fundamental principles that define our privacy policy and here they are:
✓Wordsalad generates your word clouds locally and does not transmit your text on any network to third party publishers.
✓We don’t ask you for personal information unless we truly need it.
✓We will not provide or share any mailing lists or other information about you to another company or service for promotional purposes.
✓We don’t share your personal information with anyone except to comply with the law, develop our products, or protect our rights.
✓We don’t store personal information on our servers unless required for the on-going operation of one of our services.